布什在《法伦》中表演《甘油》，宣布北美巡演https://www.nme.com/news/music/bush-perform-glycerine-fallon-gavin-rossdale-3572795?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bush-perform-glycerine-fallon-gavin-rossdaleEli Ordonez Thu, 18 Jan 2024 05:51:54 +0000 Music NewsNewsTV NewsRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3572795 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bush-gavin-rossdale@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="布什总统加文·罗斯代尔" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bush-gavin-rossdale@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bush-gavin-rossdale@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bush-gavin-rossdale@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bush-gavin-rossdale@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bush-gavin-rossdale@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bush-gavin-rossdale@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Gavin Rossdale 的表演与他 1996 年在同一节目中的曲目表演如出一辙</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bush-perform-glycerine-fallon-gavin-rossdale-3572795">布什在《Fallon》中表演《Glycerine》后，宣布北美巡演</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bush-gavin-rossdale@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="布什总统加文·罗斯代尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bush-gavin-rossdale@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bush-gavin-rossdale@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bush-gavin-rossdale@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bush-gavin-rossdale@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bush-gavin-rossdale@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/bush-gavin-rossdale@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bush">布什</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-tonight-show-starring-jimmy-fallon"><em>吉米·法伦主演的《今夜秀》</em></a>中，演唱了他们的热门歌曲“甘油”。</p><ul><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/bushs-gavin-rossdale-it-was-stupid-having-beef-with-dave-grohl-and-trent-reznor-3534911"><b>布什的加文·罗斯代尔：“与戴夫·格罗尔和特伦特·雷兹诺争吵是愚蠢的”</b></a></li></ul><p>在周二晚上（1 月 16 日）的<em>《今夜秀》</em>节目中，布什乐队的加文·罗斯代尔 (Gavin Rossdale) 在弦乐组的伴奏下独自演奏了这首歌曲。主唱手拿一把扭曲的电吉他，深情地演唱了1996年的民谣。歌曲进行到一半时，罗斯代尔停止弹吉他，以无伴奏形式唱出第二节。</p><p>请观看下面布什的“甘油”表演： </p><p><iframe title="布什：甘油|吉米·法伦主演的《今夜秀》" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tZiGfju5tdc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Bush 在<em>《今夜秀》</em>中的亮相与 1996 年他们在该节目中的亮相如出一辙，当时杰·雷诺 (Jay Leno) 担任主持人，乐队刚刚发行了他们的首张录音室专辑《十六块石头》(Sixteen Stone)。就像罗斯代尔 1 月 16 日的表演一样，他用电吉他和弦乐部分独奏了这首歌曲，周围环绕着无数的烛台。 </p><p><iframe title="布什甘油纱罗 1996" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9gx6LNnIjow?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>罗斯代尔出现在<em>Fallon</em>似乎是为了宣传 Bush 即将于今年夏天举行的“Loaded: The Greatest Hits”北美巡演， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alice-in-chains">Alice In Chains</a>吉他手 Jerry Cantrell 和 90 年代垃圾摇滚乐队 Candlebox 将担任支持演出。昨天，布什的 Instagram 帐户正式宣布了这次巡演，视频中罗斯代尔谈到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bush-share-single-nowhere-to-go-but-everywhere-and-announce-greatest-hits-album-and-us-tour-buy-tickets-3502688">他们于 11 月发行的布什精选专辑《Loaded: The Greatest Hits 1994-2023》</a>的热烈反响。</p><p> “这次巡演最好的一点是，它直接反映了人们对唱片的反应，”罗斯代尔在剪辑中说道。 “人们对最热门唱片的反应是我从未想象过的。我希望我们能够真正向您多年来所喜爱的音乐致敬，并向您给予我们的所有爱致敬。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C2KlDclrvNP/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C5